g9982PortCapTcTypesSupported OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX BITS { tc6465(0), tcHDLC(1) } MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "PTM-TC Encapsulation types supported by the G.Bond/Eth port. This is a bitmap of possible encapsulation types. The various bit positions are: tc6465 - GBS is capable of 64/65-octet encapsulation tcHDLC - GBS is capable of HDLC encapsulation
